assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Fuji Kyuko Co., Ltd. engages in transportation, tourism, distribution service, real estate, civil engineering and construction, and information technology businesses in Japan. It operates amusement parks, hotels, golf courses, ski resorts, camp grounds, etc.; and offers transportation services, including Fujikyu railway, Fujikyuko bus, share-ride buses, highway buses, reserved buses, etc., as well as real estate services, such as building leasing, condo/villa subdivision, etc. The company was incorporated in 1926 and is headquartered in Fujiyoshida, Japan.
